    ! Ticket #72: Common utils/editor/editor.hbp
    ! for WinAPI and LINUX. So editor_linux.hbp deleted.
    ! Internal Bugfix:
    ! Class HCEDIT: Ingored ~ (Tilde) on GTK/LINUX
    ! WinAPI: in MEMOEDIT of HBROWSE:
    ! Euro currency was displayed as single bar,
    ! if entered via AltGr + E, but was stored correct 
    ! in database, see sample samples/dbview.prg.
    ! Editor: Charset was fixed set to russian, now
    ! selection menu at start. Now ~ and Euro currency
    ! correct displayed and stored in file. 
    ! Documentation:
    ! - Added some description for class HFONT
    ! - Class HBROWSE: Bug info for € sign.
     

