2020-11-15 17:45 UTC+0100 Wilfried Brunken DF7BE
  * doc/hwgdoc_commands.html
    ! Ticket #57:
    ! Different behavior of hotkey marked with "&"
    ! for GTK/LINUX and WinAPI described
    ! in MENU command section.
  * samples/gtk_samples/winprn.prg
  * source/gtk/hprinter.prg
  * source/gtk/hwinprn.prg
    ! Ticket #64:
    ! Print of bitmaps now solved,
    ! because of a bug in GTK
    ! the function 
    ! gdk_pixbuf_save() does not
    ! store the bitmap correct.
    ! From hex value store
    ! in temporary file with
    ! hb_memowrit().
    ! At offsets 0x26 and 0x2a 
    ! the solution in pixels per meter
    ! is stored: for astro.bmp 0xc4 0x0e = 3780
    ! But is set to 0x0 !
    ! Also the size is not correct:
    ! The copy has more bytes.
    ! But to do :
    ! The PrintLine() method show no text, but
    ! PrintLine(10) works.  
    ! (To be continued for GTK)
  * test/gtk_test/bol.prg
    ! Test program for Ticket #69 by Alain Aupaix 

