2013-06-16 15:40 UTC+0300 Alexander Kresin <alex@belacy.belgorod.su>
  * source/debug/debugger.prg
    * Added Altd() function for xHarbour, where it is placed in debug.lib,
      borrowed from xHarbour.
  * source/xml/hxmldoc.prg
    * Two parameters added to :GetAttribute() method, it's now
      GetAttribute( cName, cType, xDefault ).
      cType, if it is set, causes conversion from a string to this
      data type ( "N", "L" ), xDefault - default value for the attribute.

