2004-03-22 18-30 UTC-0300 Rodrigo Moreno <rodrigo_moreno@yahoo.com>
  * hdialog.prg
    + Add DlgHelp event handler for help
  * hwindow.prg
    + Add HelpId property
    * Changed HWindow:New() to set the Help File Name
